Moving on

  • Grant to support UK node failed Aug 2015
  • UK now “associate member” status
  • Looking at new ways forward

Towards a new Neuro- Network:
Meeting 3 May 2016

  • Organized by Leslie Smith with funding from Wellcome Trust and eFutures.
  • Aim to relaunch the network, with focus on closer engagement with experimental/clinical areas.
  • ~60 attendees.

Key outcomes

  • Explore links with British Neuroscience Association (BNA).
  • Revisit UK data-sharing policies to strengthen neuroinformatics.
  • Exploit UK niche areas: training, clinicial neuroscience, neuro-engineering.
